data.description: Very well kept, updated triplex in SE Portland near plenty of restaurants and shops, and easy freeway access. Specs for each unit are as follows: Main unit includes 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with 1550SF, upper unit includes 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with 750SF, lower unit includes 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with 825SF. This triplex has plenty of updates with new laminate flooring, paint, stainless appliances, countertops, and much more! Includes a 2 car garage, and a second 1 car garage along with and an additional storage unit. Main unit has a great deck overlooking the yard.  Basement unit has been completely remodeled with all new flooring, cabinets, bathrooms, you name it!  Basement unit includes 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with a living space.  Unit 2 includes 2 bedrooms, 1 bath and living space as well. Yard is fully fenced with a brand new fence.
